trans-unit.source: Enables the Web programming model for a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service.

trans-unit.source: The WebHttpBehavior behavior, when used in conjunction with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding> binding, enables [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to expose and access Web style services.
trans-unit.target: WebHttpBehavior-virkemåten ved bruk sammen med den <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>binder, aktiverer [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] til å vise og få tilgang til webtjenester stil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector> maps calls to [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service operations based on the Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) suffix and the HTTP method used.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>tilordner kall til [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service operasjoner basert på Uniform URI (Resource Identifier)-suffikset og HTTP-metoden som brukes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>

trans-unit.source: This is an extensibility point that derived behaviors can use to supply their own implementation of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector> that maps the incoming HTTP request to a service operation.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en utvidelse som avledet virkemåter kan bruke til å angi sitt eget implementeringen av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>som tilordner den innkommende HTTP-forespørsler til en tjenesteoperasjon.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>

trans-unit.source: To enable the helpEnabled attribute in a configuration file: ``` <system.serviceModel> <behaviors> <endpointBehaviors> <behavior name="MyEndpointBehavior"> <webHttp helpEnabled="true" /> </behavior> </endpointBehaviors> </system.serviceModel> ``` To programmatically enable the HelpEnabled property: ``` WebHttpBehavior helpBehavior = new WebHttpBehavior(); helpBehavior.HelpEnabled = true; host.Description.Endpoints[0].Behaviors.Add(helpBehavior); ```
trans-unit.target: Aktivere attributtet helpEnabled i en konfigurasjonsfil: ``` <system.serviceModel> <behaviors> <endpointBehaviors> <behavior name="MyEndpointBehavior"> <webHttp helpEnabled="true" /> </behavior> </endpointBehaviors> </system.serviceModel> ``` du aktiverer egenskapen HelpEnabled programmatisk:``` WebHttpBehavior helpBehavior = new WebHttpBehavior(); helpBehavior.HelpEnabled = true; host.Description.Endpoints[0].Behaviors.Add(helpBehavior); ```

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Help page is enabled; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: - The binding contains an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement> where <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A> is set to `true`.
